---
title: Zero-Downtime Database Migration: Expand-Contract
---
flowchart LR
    baseline["Baseline schema<br/>App V(N-1) online"]
    expand["EXPAND<br/>Add nullable columns/tables/indexes<br/>backward compatible"]
    deploy["Deploy App V(N)<br/>Dual-read/write compatible"]
    backfill["MIGRATE<br/>Idempotent throttled backfill<br/>100M+ rows, abort >20% latency impact"]
    validate["Validate<br/>counts, checksums, synthetic transactions"]
    contract["CONTRACT<br/>Remove old columns only after approval<br/>forward-only change"]
    stable["Final schema<br/>App V(N) only + evidence"]
    rollback["Rollback/abort paths<br/>Expand reversible, migrate retryable, contract gated"]
    baseline --> expand
    expand --> deploy
    deploy --> backfill
    backfill --> validate
    validate -->|after bake + DBA approval| contract
    contract --> stable
    expand -->|failure| rollback
    backfill -->|latency/CV failure| rollback
    validate -->|data mismatch| rollback
